{"tid":1840304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來武漢肺炎係假架，北京今晚仲歌舞昇平，央視仲搞緊春晚","createTime":"2020-01-24T19:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T07:29:17.000Z","uid":230104,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"1eca7a71ffe9e20203b627f19afee15075a19f17","tid":1840304,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRYVxBE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRYVxBE.png&h=691820e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZLT3Jk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZLT3Jk.png&h=ad807915&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YX3Gu1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4YX3Gu1.png&h=108c82bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7f9086586d5149a6e979fe71d486c15d21ac71b","tid":1840304,"uid":189,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:02:23.000Z","msg":"没事儿 没事儿"},{"pid":"14ec21e07465522d5f429f7262aa21d1db54c048","tid":1840304,"uid":230104,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:03:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O_W6sU-HREU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO_W6sU-HREU&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=1a0e7e9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O_W6sU-HREU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一遍欣欣向榮，習主席英明，湖北這一刻不屬於中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef36968a634215edf45ccf4a40ea34d56bbab1e","tid":1840304,"uid":28970,"like":123,"dislike":1,"score":122,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0QvEeQW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0QvEeQW.gif&h=22ca6eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47394376dcb438b76e6482fa0840dd8611d4e936","tid":1840304,"uid":162008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:03:59.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=5ad0b5d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"09b5a7e9bf58df16112adf99e32008b3a68d969c","tid":1840304,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:05:01.000Z","msg":"白事當紅事辦係國技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfee054a37c6f1a25580bfb1114dd097d4f24b5","tid":1840304,"uid":152559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:07:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啲肺炎病毒最鍾意紅色</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6100421c78a601f3a2e46b781fa856b12264861d","tid":1840304,"uid":302894,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:08:35.000Z","msg":"切爾諾貝利4月26號爆<br />\n<br />\n4月30日下午召開的烏共中央政治局會議，討論是否取消次日的五一節活動。科學家的報告稱基輔市的放射性水平仍然是正常的。會議決定次日基輔市的五一節慶祝活動從正常的4個小時縮短到2個小時。實際情況是，5月1日風向轉變，基輔地區也遭到污染。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6140f099c28ea8c98d31c0bcac2c824405a0a8b8","tid":1840304,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:09:57.000Z","msg":"死5000萬人仲有13.5億<br />\n怕乜"},{"pid":"adfab3f613c5ddfc63acd16ec15099922e29f24f","tid":1840304,"uid":131188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:11:02.000Z","msg":"自古以來都冇武漢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f158e2c359f6490fcace19d60ad98f90a3e57a08","tid":1840304,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:19:04.000Z","msg":"錄定㗎 亞視啲friend"},{"pid":"8ca2fe6e3319ff161bbff209341da6d7e564e9cf","tid":1840304,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:24:24.000Z","msg":"太陽照常升起.jpg"},{"pid":"e9e67f84eb9cb51fdd0a4c7a71f2d95a5d6a9e36","tid":1840304,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:24:48.000Z","msg":"沒事兒，不看湖北新聞就沒事發生了，你看央視不就行了嗎？"},{"pid":"4e79b775a192d6fbb7d7dc1c4735e17f4dc3dcb2","tid":1840304,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:26:04.000Z","msg":"問我國家哪像染病<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1d46357b41e7fbc6673b60071129ccccb03f24","tid":1840304,"uid":230104,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"8ca2fe6e3319ff161bbff209341da6d7e564e9cf","tid":1840304,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco